<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/mystyle.css">
<script>
proc1 = () => {
	
	vprotocol = location.protocol;
	vhostname = location.hostname;
	vport = location.port;
	vhost = location.host;
	vpathname = location.pathname;
	vhref = location.href;
	
	str = `protocol : ${vprotocol} <br>`;
	str += `hostname : ${vhostname} <br>`;
	str += `port : ${vport} <br>`;
	str += `host : ${vhost} <br>`;
	str += `pathname : ${vpathname} <br>`;
	str += `href : ${vhref} <br>`;
	
	document.querySelector('#result1').innerHTML = str;
	
}

function proc2() {
	
	location.href = "../0510/Date객체.html"
}
</script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="box">
		<h3>location 객체<br>
		url의 정보를 가져오거나 설정</h3>
		
		<input type="button" value="확인" onclick="proc1()">
		<div id="result1" class="result"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="box">
		<h3>location 객체<br>
		location.href 사용</h3>
		
		특정 페이지로 이동할 때  
		<input type="button" value="페이지" onclick="proc2()">
		<input type="button" value="페이지" onclick="location.href='../0511/랜덤객체.html'">
		<div id="result2" class="result"></div>
		
		<br>
		a 태그를 이용
		<a href="../0509/배열문제.html">공지사항</a>
		<a href="#" onclick="proc2()">회원리스트</a>
		<a href="javascript:proc2()">회원리스트</a>
		<a href="#" onclick="location.href='../0421/입력처리1.jsp?id=a001&pw=1234'">공지사항</a> 
													   	 <!--   '?' 뒤에 공백있으면 안 됨    -->
	</div>
	
	<div class="box">
		<h3>location 객체<br>
		location.replace 사용</h3>
		
		- 새로운 문서로 대체 : 
		
		<input type="button" value="확인" onclick="location.replace('../0511/window객체.html')">
		<div id="result3" class="result"></div>
	</div>
	
</body>
</html>